      "title": "Keygeek Full Nylon Linear Switches (10PCS)",
      "handle": "keygeek-full-nylon-linear-switches-10pcs",
      "body_html": "<div>\n<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"159\"><strong>Keygeek Full Nylon</strong> Switches are linear switches, featuring a full nylon construction, these switches deliver a deeper tone and a more rounded / bassy sound. Smooth, responsive, and acoustically tuned for character, the Keygeek Full Nylon Switches are a great choice for anyone looking to elevate their keyboard with a more expressive and unique sound profile.</p>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Hand Lubing Service:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>Lube Used: Krytox 205G0</li>\n<li><span>Springs: Bag lubed with Krytox 105</span></li>\n<li>Film Used: Lume Film series - we'll cater the film type to the switch to give you the best experience possible<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>",
