      "title": "Wingtree 277 Linear Switches (10PCS)",
      "handle": "wingtree-277-linear-switches-10pcs",
      "body_html": "<p data-start=\"42\" data-end=\"178\">The <strong>Wingtree </strong><strong data-start=\"46\" data-end=\"53\">277</strong> is Wingtree’s <strong data-start=\"68\" data-end=\"96\">first-ever custom switch</strong>, designed in collaboration with WJBY Studio to go beyond typical stock offerings. As a <strong data-start=\"143\" data-end=\"163\">new manufacturer</strong>, Wingtree comes in strong with this switch. The switch features a <strong data-start=\"23\" data-end=\"62\">thicker copper leaf to reduce noise</strong><span data-start=\"23\" data-end=\"62\"> and </span>slight mold adjustments for an improved sound profile.</p>\n<p><span>We are providing personal hand lubing service, done personally by our slick in-house Lume Lubing expert.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hand Lubing Service:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>Lube Used: Krytox 205G0</li>\n<li><span>Springs: Bag lubed with Krytox 105</span></li>\n<li>Film Used: Lume Film series - we'll cater the film type to the switch to give you the best experience possible</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>",
