    {
      "id": 9307899527381,
      "title": "BSUN Mozzarella Tactile Switches (10PCS)",
      "handle": "bsun-mozzarella",
      "body_html": "<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"248\">Meet the <strong>BSUN </strong><strong data-start=\"9\" data-end=\"64\">Mozzarella Cheese Switches,</strong> a tactile switch designed by the popular HMX Cheese designer. The Mozzarella hits that sweet spot right in the middle. Not too sharp, not too subtle, just a clean, balanced tactile bump that feels satisfying without being overwhelming.</p>\n<p data-start=\"250\" data-end=\"548\">These switches feature a <strong data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"326\">mid-leaning tactility</strong>, making them perfect whether you're typing long sessions or just enjoying a smooth daily driver. The tactile event is noticeable but controlled, giving you a comfortable feedback that won’t fatigue your fingers over time.</p>\n<p><span>We are providing personal hand lubing service, done personally by our slick in-house Lume Lubing expert.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hand Lubing Service:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>Lube Used: Krytox 205G0</li>\n<li><span>Springs: Bag lubed with Krytox 105</span></li>\n<li>Film Used: Lume Film series - we'll cater the film type to the switch to give you the best experience possible</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>",
      "published_at": "2026-03-27T22:08:36-07:00",
