    {
      "id": 9307892154581,
      "title": "HMX Aperol switch Linear Switches (10PCS)",
      "handle": "hmx-aperol-switch-linear-switches-10pcs",
      "body_html": "<p data-end=\"229\" data-start=\"48\">The HMX Aperol is one of the <strong data-end=\"116\" data-start=\"84\">clackiest switches out there</strong>. Built with a <strong data-end=\"143\" data-start=\"131\">POM stem</strong> and HMX’s new <strong data-end=\"179\" data-start=\"158\">P7 bottom housing</strong>, it delivers a loud, sharp, and satisfying clack.</p>\n<p data-end=\"462\" data-start=\"231\">The Aperol pushes the sound to the next level with P7 material which is <strong data-end=\"298\" data-start=\"252\">new nylon blend </strong>(PA66 with 50% fiberglass), a big jump from older blends like P2 or P3, which already sounded clacky with less fiberglass. If you want a <strong data-end=\"521\" data-start=\"478\">super crisp, loud, and aggressive clack</strong>, this one won’t disappoint.</p>\n<p><span>We are providing personal hand lubing service, done personally by our slick in-house Lume Lubing expert.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hand Lubing Service:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>Lube Used: Krytox 205G0</li>\n<li><span>Springs: Bag lubed with Krytox 105</span></li>\n<li>Film Used: Lume Film series - we'll cater the film type to the switch to give you the best experience possible</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>",
      "published_at": "2026-03-25T22:41:18-07:00",
